### Booking API Tests

@baseUrl = http://localhost:4000/api
@token = YOUR_AUTH_TOKEN_HERE
@eventId = 1
@tierId = 1

### 1. Get Event for Booking (Public)
GET {{baseUrl}}/booking/events/{{eventId}}

### 2. Get Seat Status (SEAT_MAP events only)
GET {{baseUrl}}/booking/events/{{eventId}}/tiers/{{tierId}}/seats

### 3. Calculate Price (without promo)
POST {{baseUrl}}/booking/calculate-price
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "eventId": {{eventId}},
    "tierId": {{tierId}},
    "quantity": 2
}

### 4. Calculate Price (with promo)
POST {{baseUrl}}/booking/calculate-price
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "eventId": {{eventId}},
    "tierId": {{tierId}},
    "quantity": 2,
    "promoCode": "SAVE10"
}

### 5. Validate Promo Code
POST {{baseUrl}}/booking/validate-promo
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "code": "SAVE10",
    "eventId": {{eventId}}
}

### 6. Lock Seats (SEAT_MAP events)
POST {{baseUrl}}/booking/lock-seats
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "eventId": {{eventId}},
    "tierId": {{tierId}},
    "seatNumbers": ["S1", "S2"]
}

### 7. Release Seats
POST {{baseUrl}}/booking/release-seats
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "eventId": {{eventId}},
    "tierId": {{tierId}},
    "seatNumbers": ["S1", "S2"]
}

### 8. Create Reservation (CAPACITY event)
POST {{baseUrl}}/booking/reserve
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "eventId": {{eventId}},
    "tierId": {{tierId}},
    "quantity": 2,
    "paymentMethod": "CHAPA"
}

### 9. Create Reservation (SEAT_MAP event with promo)
POST {{baseUrl}}/booking/reserve
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "eventId": {{eventId}},
    "tierId": {{tierId}},
    "quantity": 2,
    "seatNumbers": ["S1", "S2"],
    "paymentMethod": "CHAPA",
    "promoCode": "SAVE10"
}

### 10. Extend Lock Time
# Replace 1 with actual purchaseId
POST {{baseUrl}}/booking/1/extend
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 11. Cancel Reservation
# Replace 1 with actual purchaseId
POST {{baseUrl}}/booking/1/cancel
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
